{"tid":1223752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺身邊好多人都鬆懈晒 好似成功左咁","createTime":"2019-06-14T19:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:26:10.000Z","uid":41411,"like":151,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"12418f0ab4b52ef0da5f15922dbf718b29e9e76f","tid":1223752,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:11:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊記我地乜野都未爭取到呀！<br />\n係負數呀！有好多義士比人拉撚左 <br />\n又中槍 食棍 食催淚彈 食胡椒噴霧<br />\n立法會仲有機會係星期一復會！<br />\n如果大家因為依2日休會就鬆懈晒 帶來既後果就只係大家唔再齊心去反惡法！最後就一齊被送中！<br />\n所以星期日一定要出黎遊行 叫晒身邊所有人！<br />\n要比6月9號更多人！要比全世界知道香港人唔會因為你班黑警開幾多十槍而懼縮！</span>"},{"pid":"115d2eb5d7bdb04f51283c5b08df403b3cc40ccc","tid":1223752,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa502c3796d5821d561a3c6184b85c1a1061375","tid":1223752,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddecf2d13b332a613fa040c4bc02dd51be5f2842","tid":1223752,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:18:40.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！"},{"pid":"f495fe17ab423b7da98e1484b251056abcb2a5a3","tid":1223752,"uid":260184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b060e70b3d580a220ff2939f77ce00c93a22f57","tid":1223752,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T1